<section class="HeroSection {{#if optional_classes}}{{optional_classes}}{{/if}}" {{#if id}}id="{{id}}"{{/if}}>
    <div class="HeroSection-image">
        {{#if content.image}}
            {{> 'responsiveImage/responsiveImage' image=content.image alt=content.header title=content.header}}
        {{/if}}
    </div>
    <div class="HeroSection-content-wrapper">
        <div class="HeroSection-content {{#if content.position}}{{content.position}}{{/if}} {{#if content.text_align}}{{content.text_align}}{{/if}}">
            <h2>{{content.header}}</h2>
            <div class="HeroSection-content__copy">{{{content.copy_text}}}</div>
            <a class="cta" href="{{content.link.url}}" {{#if content.link.target}}target="{{content.link.target}}"{{/if}}>{{content.link.text}}</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{{!

Description:
The position for the content and the text alignment can optionally be set for mobile and desktop individually.
Starting from mobile, if only one value gets specified, it will apply to all screen-sizes.
If the positioning/alignment for desktop should differ, add the desktop value as additional parameter.

